    <item>
      <title>巴克莱前财富主管因误导 FCA 被禁止任职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-27/ex-barclays-wealth-chief-barred-from-job-for-misleading-watchdog</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴克莱银行前财富主管汤姆·卡拉里斯（Tom Kalaris）未能获得担任英国金融业高级职位的批准，此前伦敦一家法院宣布，在被问及该银行与卡塔尔有争议的融资活动时，他存在不诚实行为。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-27/ex-barclays-wealth-chief-barred-from-job-for-misleading-watchdog</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 11:23:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>IPO 候选人的困境：趁着秋季上市还是等到 2025 年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-27/the-ipo-hopeful-s-dilemma-cram-into-fall-window-or-wait-for-25</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着秋季 IPO 窗口打开，渴望上市的公司面临着一个艰难的选择：趁着市场接近历史高点时趁机上市，还是等到明年，届时利率和美国大选风险将会消退。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-27/the-ipo-hopeful-s-dilemma-cram-into-fall-window-or-wait-for-25</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由 Bob Diamond 支持的 SPAC 签署合并协议，将 Events.com 上市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-27/bob-diamond-led-spac-said-to-be-near-merger-with-events-com</link>
      <description><![CDATA[活动管理平台 Events.com 已达成协议，将与 Bob Diamond 和 Jeff Tuder 领导的空白支票公司合并，合并后的企业价值预计接近 4 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-27/bob-diamond-led-spac-said-to-be-near-merger-with-events-com</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 05:00:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
